trans-unit.source: Marks the attributed method as an <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> object.
If `AutoComplete` is specified, it must not be disabled in the COM+ catalog; if enabled in the COM+ catalog, it must be specified on the component.
The transaction automatically calls <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ContextUtil.SetComplete%2A> if the method call returns normally.
If the method call throws an exception, the transaction is aborted.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"></xref> class, specifying that the application should automatically call <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ContextUtil.SetComplete*> if the transaction completes successfully.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.AutoCompleteAttribute"></xref> class, specifying whether COM+ <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> is enabled.
Specifying a parameter value of `false` causes the `AutoComplete` attribute to be ignored.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to enable <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> in the COM+ object; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets a value indicating the setting of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> option in COM+.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if <xref uid="langword_csharp_AutoComplete" name="AutoComplete" href=""></xref> is enabled in COM+; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
